When we touch– our bodies release “feel good” hormones. These hormones include oxytocin, dopamine, and serotonin. The hormones make us experience feelings of happiness, relaxation, improve mood, and lower levels of depression. @ScottMorrisonMP @PeterDutton_MP #LoveIsNotTourism
